      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for daily commuting, though it does show its age. The exterior features several noticeable scratches and a few minor dings, while the interior upholstery exhibits some wear and fading from regular use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it may require minor cosmetic attention or routine maintenance soon to keep it in peak form. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at an accessible price point.",
