    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it is time for a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been garage-kept, regularly detailed, and runs like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for your next adventure, you\u2019ve found it. You've really gotta see this one in person to believe it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
