      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to put my absolute pride and joy up for sale. Honestly, this car is a total dream\u2014it's in stunning condition and looks just as good as the day I first got it! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it sparkling clean and running perfectly. It\u2019s super smooth to drive and has been loved every single mile. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been truly babied and is ready to hit the road today, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_20_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level 2004 BMW M3, a definitive expression of the E46 platform. Under the hood, the S54 3.2L inline-six remains a masterpiece of atmospheric induction, featuring individual throttle bodies and a meticulously maintained dual-VANOS system for optimal cam phasing. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing tactile engagement through every gate. The chassis has been professionally reinforced at the subframe mounting points to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. Handling is sharpened by a refreshed suspension featuring factory-spec dampers and bushings, while the variable M differential lock ensures precise torque distribution. Finished in Carbon Black with a pristine Cinnamon Nappa leather interior, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the discerning collector seeking peak mechanical and aesthetic integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
